freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Developed a cough a week ago, an intermittent headache and a drippy nose. Having a covid test tomorrow.

My asthma flared up after 20 years of it being well controlled.  It took almost 5 weeks to get it under control and i believe the covid vaccines caused it to happen. It was a struggle and 2 doctor visits.
